          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Are the products official?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>At ForgeBall 3D, we offer high-quality products. With impeccable details and unbeatable prices, our products are authentic and provide a superior experience in every detail. We guarantee that every item delivered meets our high standards, so you receive products that represent your passion with excellence and durability.<\/p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_AY9XMK": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "If I don't like it, can I return it?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>In cases of regret or dissatisfaction, you may request the return of the product within 7 calendar days from receipt, as provided for in the Consumer Protection Code.<\/p><p><em>Important:<\/em> Personalized products (with name, number or any modification requested by the customer) cannot be exchanged or refunded, except in cases of manufacturing defects.<\/p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_FbyYkq": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How to choose the right size?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>To make the right purchase, always consult our Size Guide. If in doubt, choose a size larger than you normally wear, this way you guarantee more comfort, freedom of movement and avoid surprises when getting dressed.<\/p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_FBpGM4": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is it safe to buy from ForgeBall 3D?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Our store is recommended by Trustpilot. Since 2024, we have delivered over 20,000 orders worldwide, building a two-year track record of experience, quality, and dedication. Don't hesitate to buy your shirts from us and join the thousands of passionate fan customers.<\/p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_Bcw3XX": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How does delivery work?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Our shipments are directly from Asia. Upon completing your order, we will ship it within 2 to 5 days. After shipment, you will receive your tracking code in your registered email to track your order until delivery. Our average delivery time is 5 to 15 business days.<br\/><br\/><a href=\"\/policies\/shipping-policy\" title=\"\/policies\/shipping-policy\"><em>Please see our delivery policies for more information.<\/em><\/a><\/p>",
            "page": ""
          }
